description.en:
BitcoinSubsidium (XBTX) is a complementary coin to TELOS and also part of the Transcendence Blockchain OpenSource project.

Unlike TELOS which uses POS and Masternodes, XBTX uses POW and ASIC-resistant. Its effective to be mined only using CPU power.
